Grafit is written in Python (http://www.python.org/) and uses:

Numeric          http://numpy.sourceforge.net/
PyQt             http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/pyqt/
PyQwt            http://pyqwt.sourceforge.net/
QScintilla       http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/qscintilla/

(The following are included in lib-sources)
# odr              http://starship.python.net/crew/kernr/Projects.html
# mimetex          http://www.forkosh.com/mimetex.html
